snippet.title: Best VGM 1468 - Gremlins 2 : The New Batch - Stage 3
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 175 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w2HT5XkGaws

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Gremlins 2 : The New Batch (1990)
Stage 3
Nobuyuki Hara, Shinichi Seya & Naoki Kodaka
